to those conferences,

08:49.625 --> 08:52.333
I wanted it in the back of his mind
that he had a wife

08:52.417 --> 08:54.834
with a loaded Smith and Wesson.

08:54.917 --> 08:58.166
Lynnie, Tom's always away.
Do you ever worry he might...?

08:58.250 --> 09:02.000
He's gotten me pregnant
three times in four years.

09:02.083 --> 09:04.583
