What do you do?

11:22.583 --> 11:26.458
Plumber. So if you ever have a clog...

11:27.750 --> 11:29.375
...or something.

11:33.291 --> 11:36.417
Now that everybody's seen
that I brought something,

11:36.542 --> 11:39.792
I should probably just throw this out.

11:50.583 --> 11:52.875
Ease up, you little vampire.

11:55.291 --> 11:59.125
Lynette, I've been looking
all over for you.

11:59.208 --> 12:01.667
Are you aware
of what your sons are doing?

12:01.792 --> 12:04.125
Cannonball.

12:07.125 --> 12:09.250
Stop.

12:14.709 --> 12:17.667
What are you doing? We are at a wake.

12:17.792 --> 12:22.417
- You said we could go in the pool.
- I said you could go by the pool.

12:23.083 --> 12:24.792
Do you have your swimsuits on?

12:24.875 --> 12:27.792
Yeah, we put 'em on ourselves
before we left.

12:27.917 --> 12:31.250
You three planned this? All right.
That's it. Get out.

12:31.333 --> 12:33.583
- No.
- No?

12:33.667 --> 12:37.542
I am your mother.
You have to do what I say. Come on.

12:37.667 --> 12:40.959
We want to swim and you can't stop us.

12:49.875 --> 12:51.667
Here.

12:53.291 --> 12:54.667
