- Get out.

12:54.792 --> 12:58.417
Think I won't get in this pool
and just grab you? Get out.

13:01.000 --> 13:03.333
Get over here.

13:04.375 --> 13:06.917
All right, give me your arm.

13:12.208 --> 13:14.458
That's right. Get over here.

13:14.542 --> 13:16.917
Go. Move it.

13:24.542 --> 13:26.375
Out. Get out.

13:33.875 --> 13:38.667
Paul, we have to leave now.
Once again, I am so sorry for your loss.

13:40.542 --> 13:42.375
Go.

13:42.500 --> 13:45.834
<i>Lynette shouldn't have been</i>
<i>so concerned about my husband.</i>

13:45.917 --> 13:51.500
<i>He had other things on his mind.</i>
<i>Things below the surface.</i>

13:59.417 --> 14:03.500
<i>The morning after my funeral, my friends</i>
<i>and neighbors quietly went back</i>

14:03.583 --> 14:05.792
<i>to their busy, busy lives.</i>

14:06.917 --> 14:09.375
<i>While some did their cooking</i>

14:11.458 --> 14:14.208
<i>and some did their cleaning</i>

14:15.500 --> 14:17.583
<i>and some did their yoga</i>

14:18.250 --> 14:21.166
