about my love life.

15:05.625 --> 15:07.917
I wouldn't have said anything. Just...

15:08.000 --> 15:09.333
What?

15:10.125 --> 15:14.083
I heard Dad's girlfriend ask
if you'd dated anyone since the divorce.

15:14.166 --> 15:19.959
And Dad said he doubted it.
And then they both laughed.

15:35.458 --> 15:37.250
Hey, Susan.

15:37.333 --> 15:40.000
Hi, Mike. I brought you
a house-warming gift.

15:40.917 --> 15:43.667
I should've brought
something by earlier.

15:43.750 --> 15:46.750
- Actually, you're the first to stop by.
- Really?

15:46.834 --> 15:48.834
<i>- Susan knew she was lucky.</i>
- Well...

15:48.917 --> 15:51.750
<i>An eligible bachelor</i>
<i>had moved on to Wisteria Lane</i>

15:51.834 --> 15:53.792
<i>and she was the first to find out.</i>

15:53.875 --> 15:56.208
<i>She also knew that good news...</i>

15:56.333 --> 15:58.667
- Hello, there.
<i>- ...travels quickly.</i>

15:58.750 --> 16:03.125
<i>Edie Britt was the most predatory</i>
<i>divorcée in a five-block radius.</i>

16:04.208 --> 16:06.542
<i>Her conquests were numerous.</i>

16:08.709 --> 16:10.458
<i>Varied.</i>

16:12.208 --> 16:14.000
<i>And legendary.</i>

16:16.375 --> 16:19.875
Hi, Susan. I hope I'm not interrupting.

16:21.333 --> 16:25.125
You must be Mike Delfino.
Hi, I'm Edie Britt.

16:25.208 --> 16:27.083
I live over there.

16:27.208 --> 16:29.542
Welcome to Wisteria Lane.

16:30.125 --> 16:33.875
<i>Susan had met the enemy.</i>
<i>And she was a slut.</i>

16:33.959 --> 16:35.959
Thank you. What's this?

16:36.041 --> 16:39.917
Sausage <i>puttanesca.</i>
