but I was in the middle of something.

16:47.583 --> 16:50.583
- I'm late for an appointment.
- I just wanted to say hi.

16:50.709 --> 16:54.834
<i>And just like that,</i>
<i>the race for Mike Delfino had begun.</i>

16:54.917 --> 16:57.917
<i>For a moment, Susan wondered</i>
<i>if her rivalry with Edie</i>

16:58.041 --> 16:59.667
<i>would remain friendly.</i>

16:59.750 --> 17:03.208
Oh, Mike, I heard you're a plumber.

17:03.333 --> 17:06.083
<i>But she was reminded that</i>
<i>when it came to men...</i>

17:06.208 --> 17:09.625
Could you stop by later
and take a look at my pipes?

17:09.709 --> 17:12.166
<i>- ...women don't fight fair.</i>
- Sure.

17:13.417 --> 17:14.917
Thanks.

17:20.125 --> 17:22.375
Bye, Susan.

17:22.458 --> 17:25.208
- You can't order me around.
- Gabrielle.

17:25.333 --> 17:26.583
No, I'm not going.

17:26.667 --> 17:29.750
