You were meant to dig it up.

17:55.500 --> 17:57.875
- I didn't have time.
- I don't want excuses.

17:57.959 --> 18:00.041
Just take care of it.

18:02.375 --> 18:05.333
I really hate the way you talk to me.

18:05.417 --> 18:08.667
And I hate that I spent $15,000
on your diamond necklace

18:08.750 --> 18:10.333
you couldn't live without.

18:10.458 --> 18:15.500
But I'm learning to deal with it. So can
I tell Tanaka we'll be there tomorrow?

18:15.583 --> 18:19.583
John, we have bandages
top shelf in the kitchen.

18:19.667 --> 18:21.000
Thanks, Mrs. Solis.

18:25.667 --> 18:27.500
Fine, I'll go.

18:27.625 --> 18:31.166
